---
// Honest "How we research / Sources" block for E-E-A-T. Reusable across money
// pages and key articles. States the real editorial process (primary-source
// research, pen-name team, review + correction) and lists the primary sources
// this site draws on. No fabricated credentials, no invented data. Bilingual via
// URL-derived lang. Optional `sources` prop overrides the default source list
// with page-specific primary sources (kept generic + verifiable).
import { getLangFromUrl } from '../i18n/ui';

interface Props {
  // Optional page-specific source labels (e.g. 'IRS Form W-7 instructions').
  sources?: string[];
}
const { sources } = Astro.props;
const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const isEs = lang === 'es';

const defaultSources = isEs
  ? ['el IRS', 'la CFPB', 'la FTC', 'FICO', 'Experian, Equifax y TransUnion', 'los materiales publicados por los emisores de tarjetas']
  : ['the IRS', 'the CFPB', 'the FTC', 'FICO', 'Experian, Equifax & TransUnion', "card issuers' published materials"];
const list = sources && sources.length ? sources : defaultSources;

const heading = isEs ? 'Cómo investigamos esta página' : 'How we researched this page';
const policyHref = isEs ? '/es/editorial-policy' : '/editorial-policy';
const policyLabel = isEs ? 'política editorial' : 'editorial policy';
---
<aside class="sources-note">
  <p class="sources-note-h">{heading}</p>
  {isEs ? (
    <p class="sources-note-b">
      Esta guía la escribió y revisó nuestro equipo editorial a partir de fuentes
      primarias, {list.join(', ')}, en lugar de otros blogs. Las cifras, tarifas y
      requisitos se cotejan con esa documentación antes de publicar; los términos
      específicos de cada tarjeta cambian, así que verifícalos con el emisor. No
      inventamos estadísticas, probabilidades de aprobación ni términos de
      producto. Lee nuestra <a href={policyHref}>{policyLabel}</a> completa.
    </p>
  ) : (
    <p class="sources-note-b">
      This guide was written and reviewed by our editorial team using primary
      sources, {list.join(', ')}, rather than other blogs. Figures, fees, and
      requirements are checked against that documentation before publishing;
      card-specific terms change, so verify them with the issuer. We don't invent
      statistics, approval odds, or product terms. Read our full
      <a href={policyHref}>{policyLabel}</a>.
    </p>
  )}
</aside>

<style>
  .sources-note {
    margin: 26px 0;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border, #E7E2F2);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary, #5B21B6);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--surface, #F7F5FC);
  }
  .sources-note-h {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--primary-dark, #4C1D95);
  }
  .sources-note-b {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--muted, #5C5470);
  }
</style>
